    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p><b><span class="error">&#91;Description&#93;</span></b><br/>
According to U5Lx Hardware User Manual version 1.02.<br/>
MCU module has to support init Retention RAM section following HWM.</p>

<p><b><span class="error">&#91;Impact to Customer/User&#93;</span></b> <br/>
Event: When user configure parameter 'McuRamSectionSize' initial size from ‘McuRamSectionBaseAddress' is scoped for Retention RAM,<br/>
User cannot initialize the RAM section for Retention RAM successfully as provided from the RAM Sector setting when invoking Mcu_InitRamSection API.</p>

<p><b><span class="error">&#91;Issue Condition&#93;</span></b><br/>
In container McuRamSectorSettingConf:<br/>
+McuRamDefaultValue = 0<br/>
+McuRamSectionBaseAddress = 0x2C000000<br/>
+McuRamSectionSize = 4<br/>
+McuRamSectionWriteSize = 4</p>
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <br/>

